data.description: Don't miss, the one you have been waiting for is available now. This beautiful 5 bedroom pool home features fresh exterior paint and newer 6' privacy fence. The owners suite is huge and boasts walk in shower with separate soaker tub, two separate walk in closets and double vanity.  The Screened in pool is amazing.  The home features a formal living area open to the front entry. The natural lighting flows through the large open concept  island kitchen and living room, both with pool views. The island kitchen also features upgraded granite counter tops. The island is pre-plumbed for an additional kosher/prep sink and the kitchen has two separate pantries as well. The lot next door is for sale as well if you need a double lot! Call now for private showing.
